Classes that process console requests.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AbstractAction Base class for all actions.
ActionRegistry The ActionRegistry can be used to locate actions for a given action name.
CollapsedResultViewAction Renders Top Level EtmPoints Only.
DetailAction Base class for all actions.
ExpandedResultViewAction Renders all measurement results.
RedirectAction Redirects to a given target.
ResetMonitorAction Resets current measurement results.
ResourceAction Resource a certain resource.
StartMonitorAction Starts performance monitoring.
StatusCodeAction Renders a status code.
StopMonitorAction Disable performance monitoring.
